**Apocalyptic Cupid** | Unaligned Align - Townsfolk Base Alignment
__Basics__
The Apocalyptic Cupid is a cupid whose lover is a member of the horsemen team.
__Details__
If the cupid selects a lover from the horsemen team, or if their lover joins the horsemen team, the cupid turns into a Apocalyptic Cupid.
The Apocalyptic Cupid works like the cupid, with an exception: The Apocalyptic Cupid cannot be killed by the horsemen.
If any horseman attacks or attempts to kill the Apocalyptic Cupid the attack/kill fails.
The Apocalyptic Cupid's win condition is not changed.

__Simplified__
The Apocalyptic Cupid is a cupid whose lover is a member of the horsemen team. The Apocalyptic Cupid's base alignment is Townsfolk.
